﻿/*
Multi100 Project - Step 2
Analyst ID: DAA9C

Prompt: 
Your analysis should produce a single, main result in terms of statistical families of z-, t-, F-, or χ² tests (or their alternative or non-parametric versions).
Use only the data of Illinois Plumbing Firms in your model. 
Do not restrict your sample to those firms that serve the metro Chicago area. 
Do not include the reviews received via yelp.com, Angie’s List, and Consumer’s Checkbook into your analysis. 
